{"tid":351873,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"教你整白切雞！","createTime":"2017-08-08T11:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T11:41:12.000Z","uid":41205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"92efaae77efe988d1c5d494a7ef9c8e469ab9aaa","tid":351873,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:37:23.000Z","msg":"女新移民被斬213刀謀殺案　男友見避孕套　揭女友與小巴司機偷情<br />\n<br />\n新移民失婚女，與一名由內地帶女兒到港定居的已婚男在港共賦同居，但女方又與一名小巴司機搭上，更帶小巴司機到住所「偷歡」。同居男友在家中及住所附近垃圾桶找到「用過」避孕套，大興問罪下，涉嫌狂斬213刀令女友致死。同居男子今在高院否認一項謀殺罪名，案件開審。控方將於下午傳召死者情夫出庭作供。<br />\n<br />\n已婚被告到港後與女友同居<br />\n<br />\n控方開案陳詞透露，楊於2000年與一名男子於內地結婚，育有一女，2007年她獲得香港身份證，並與丈夫離婚，返回內地居住。翌年楊在內地認識了被告，並和被告同居。<br />\n<br />\n控方透露，被告亦為一名已婚漢，育有一女，2004年獲准來港定居，但不久返回內地居住。2009年4月被告和女兒來港定居，與楊於涉案單位同居，被告在港擔任散工工作，楊則在一間便利店擔任早更職員，因而認識駕小巴司機陳北勝，並開始約會，不久發展性關係。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/110563?utm_content=bufferc5ae1&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fsns%2Farticle%2F110563%3Futm_content%3Dbufferc5ae1%26utm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%2Bhk01%26utm_campaign%3Dbuffer&d=wAxuK3IIaKUC0PTKA8tUdbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=4a0a8bae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/sns/article/110563?utm_content=bufferc5ae1&amp;utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=facebook+hk01&amp;utm_campaign=buffer</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cdadf75d90822deea5a4093250c46bd9f7b3a2e","tid":351873,"uid":42569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:40:08.000Z","msg":"笑"},{"pid":"a31386997dc4c886ef2bfda4431de745d5a6ccac","tid":351873,"uid":41205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"要斬213刀少d臂力都唔得啊"}]}